Fairfield Grammar School was a secondary school in Bristol , England , founded in 1898 as Fairfield Secondary and Higher Grade School .
It became a grammar school in 1945 and closed in 2000 , to be replaced by a new comprehensive , Fairfield High School , at first on the same site , but now located in Stottbury Road , Bristol .
BHES -LRB- Bristol Hospital Education Service -RRB- , is now based in half of the old school , the other half is used by a similar service for under 13s .